content: Love it. Great quick readings for any and every path crossed in this life. Thank you so much.
Love it!
I really enjoy this company's tarot reading applications. It is a great educational resource for abstract analysis and divination.

This is wild. I was pretty skeptical about a tarot app. I tried it and wow. Truly works. Several awesome features especially if you physically own the deck. Super helpful and easy quick reference for the cards. Several options to use different cards. Several layouts and meanings. Seriously epic app if you're looking for a legitimate one. I can't think of anything to make it better. Great job!
Love this deck. Didn't think it would really work because it was digital and its been amazing how on Q it is with every single reading

Very happy with this app. Recently purchased these cards irl and having the digital booklet as well as something to learn and explore new spreads is great. I especially love the journal part of it so you can take notes of your own interpretation of the cards!
This is my favorite Tarot deck so far for digital. Still hoping one day they end up adding Anne Stokes Legends to the digital collection. But right now I use this more than even my physical cards.
I'm loving the app. It's easy to use & I can give myself a reading in the evening on my tablet without putting my light on! Beautiful artwork as well
